Week 1: Foundations of AI — How Machines Learn and Communicate

📋 Overview
Week 1 lays the groundwork for understanding AI from first principles. Rather than jumping straight into tools and tricks, this week covers what AI actually is, how it evolved, and how to communicate with it effectively — spanning the history of neural networks all the way to hands-on prompt engineering techniques used by practitioners today.
